@{b}Mind Peel@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Sorcery
Cost    = B
Artist  = Adam Rex

Text(SH): Buyback 2BB (You may pay an additional 2BB when you play this
          spell. If you do, put it into your hand instead of your graveyard
          as part of the spell's effect.)
          Target player chooses and discards a card.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node MINDW "Mindwarper"

@{b}Mindwarper@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Summon Spirit (0/0)
Cost    = 2BB
Artist  = Paolo Parente

Text(SH): Mindwarper comes into play with three +1/+1 counters on it.
          <2B>, Remove a +1/+1 counter from Mindwarper: Target player
          chooses and discards a card. Play this ability as a sorcery.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node MORGU "Morgue Thrull"

@{b}Morgue Thrull@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Summon Thrull (2/2)
Cost    = 2B
Artist  = Robert Bliss

Text(SH): Sacrifice Morgue Thrull: Put the top three cards of your library
          into your graveyard.

Flavor Text: @{i}It's so hard to find good help these days.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node MORTU "Mortuary"

@{b}Mortuary@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 3B
Artist  = Robert Bliss

Text(SH): Whenever any creature is put into your graveyard from play, put
          that creature on top of your library.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Think of them not as failures but as works in progress."
              -Volrath@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
