@{b}Rabid Rats@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Summon Rats (1/1)
Cost    = 1B
Artist  = Natthew Wilson

Text(SH): <T>: Target blocking creature gets -1/-1 until end of turn.

Flavor Text: @{i}Every sentence in Volrath's prisons ends the same way.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node REVEN "Revenant"

@{b}Revenant@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Summon Spirit (/)
Cost    = 4B
Artist  = Terese Nielson

Text(SH): Flying
          Revenant has power and toughness each equal to the number of
          creature cards in your graveyard.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Not again." -Hans@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
