@{b}Serpent Warrior@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Summon Soldier (3/3)
Cost    = 2B
Artist  = Ron Spencer

Text(SH): When Serpent Warrior comes into play, lose 3 life.

Flavor Text: @{i}A hiss before dying.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node SKELE "Skeleton Scavengers"

@{b}Skeleton Scavengers@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Summon Skeletons (0/0)
Cost    = 2B
Artist  = Brian Snoddy

Text(SH): Skeleton Scavengers comes into play with one +1/+1 counter on it.
          Pay 1 for each +1/+1 counter on Skeleton Scavengers: Regenerate
          Skeleton Scavengers and put a +1/+1 counter on it.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
