@{b}Stronghold Assassin@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Summon Assassin (2/1)
Cost    = 1BB
Artist  = Matthew Wilson

Text(SH): <T>, Sacrifice a creature: Destroy target nonblack creature.

Flavor Text: @{i}The assassin sees only throats and hears only heartbeats.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node STROT "Stronghold Taskmaster"

@{b}Stronghold Taskmaster@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Summon Minion (4/3)
Cost    = 2BB
Artist  = Brom

Text(SH): All other black creatures get -1/-1.

Flavor Text: @{i}"With the completion of each joyous task, we are closer to
              Yawgmoth's divine vision." -Stronghold architect, journal@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
