@{b}Torment@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Enchant Creature
Cost    = 1B
Artist  = Paolo Parente

Text(SH): Enchanted creature gets -3/-0.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Volrath has killed me. All that remains of me is the scar!"
              -Tahngarth@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node TORTU "Tortured Existence"

@{b}Tortured Existence@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = B
Artist  = Keith Parkinson

Text(SH): <B>, Choose and discard a creature card. Return target creature
          card from your graveyard to your hand.

Flavor Text: @{i}"There are terors lurking in the unseen corners of us all."
              -Crovax@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node WALLO "Wall of Souls"

@{b}Wall of Souls@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Summon Wall (0/4)
Cost    = 1B
Artist  = John Matson

Text(SH): (Walls cannot attack.)
          Whenever Wall of Souls is dealt combat damage, it deals an equal
          amount of damage to target opponent.

Flavor Text: @{i}"It is the nature of evil to turn you against yourself."
              -Starke@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

